Package: rfaScrape
Title: Scrape and export sqlite files from RFA
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Dan", "McGraw", , "daniel.e.mcgraw@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A system to scrape and export RFA project data from .sqlite files
    using the `DBI` and `RSQLite` packages. Provide the path to the RFA .sqlite file
    and `rfaScrape` will read the file and export the data to organized
    directories. This package will support 'rfaR' in the future.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/danmcgraw94/rfaScrape
BugReports: https://github.com/danmcgraw94/rfaScrape/issues
Imports:
    DBI,
    dplyr,
    fst,
    RSQLite,
    tidyr
Suggests: 
